WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.080
♪ Anyway it's your show ♪

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:07.580
♪ You're gonna party till the party's all gone ♪

00:00:07.589 --> 00:00:11.709
People that lived in shacks, in the place
they called Bloody Bucket,

00:00:11.709 --> 00:00:15.259
and the other side of the tracks that was
the most interesting.

00:00:15.259 --> 00:00:21.830
♪ Driving to Montgomery where the times
have changed ♪

00:00:21.830 --> 00:00:25.090
We vowed only to play black music.

00:00:25.090 --> 00:00:28.420
And that was what we loved: James Brown and
Otis Redding.

00:00:28.420 --> 00:00:31.220
I guess we wanted to be black.

00:00:31.220 --> 00:00:34.480
[music]

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:38.760
We had finished the Gregg Allman record and
Greg wanted to go on tour.

00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:44.149
It was like yeah, I'll do it. I just won't
worry about having a solo career.

00:00:44.149 --> 00:00:48.049
♪ I'm coming back down to Earth ♪

00:00:48.049 --> 00:00:50.820
♪ Wherever that is ♪

00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:55.840
And we were starting to realize we were not
on the cutting edge anymore.

00:00:55.840 --> 00:01:05.280
♪ There are gifts of desperation everywhere
♪

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:08.440
It's better for me to be alive than dead.

00:01:08.440 --> 00:01:10.680
That's what it comes down to.

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:13.200
Playing music and die, you know, that's stupid.

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:17.520
♪ Roll, roll, roll, everybody got to roll
♪

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:20.639
About halfway through school, I get this call
from Steve Winwood's people.

00:01:20.639 --> 00:01:24.889
They're like, hey, you want to join this tour?

00:01:24.889 --> 00:01:28.229
Steve wants you to be in the band.

00:01:28.229 --> 00:01:32.840
♪ You'll understand it all one day ♪

00:01:32.849 --> 00:01:33.869
Roger really liked it.

00:01:33.869 --> 00:01:38.800
He contacted me and said I want you to sing some on my solo thing, and help me write some too

00:01:38.800 --> 00:01:40.500
So I said sure.

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:44.359
♪ Who used to rule the world ♪

00:01:44.359 --> 00:01:48.840
I remember Bonnie playing on the same show
as us with Sea Level.

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:53.580
You know, we would play shows together…before
she got too big.

00:01:53.580 --> 00:01:55.080
We got smaller.

00:01:55.080 --> 00:01:58.760
♪ You're gonna party till the party's all
gone ♪

00:01:58.760 --> 00:02:07.600
[vocal scatting]

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:16.760
♪ Till the party's all gone ♪

00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:24.360
♪ Til the party's all gone, yeah, yeah ♪

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:34.000
[applause]

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:36.520
Thank you so much.

